Solution:
Since $\triangle RPS$ is a right triangle, $\sin \angle RPS = \sin (\angle RPQ + \angle QPS).$

[asy]
pair R,P,Q,SS;
SS = (-2,0);
P = (0,0);
Q = (2,0);
R = rotate(aSin(7/25))*(1.5,0);
